     H            Y.
     F*** AH#R3I **********************************
     F*  ..Ａ－ＰＩＣＳかんばん調査リストＮＯ４ *
     F*       臨時かんばんデータ抽出            *
     F*       MSK.KUNIEDA       99.11.19          *
     F******************************** AH#R3I *****
     FAH#WP34 IP  E           K        DISK
     FADATL60 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAH#WP3I O   F     120            DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80AHYMD
     I                                        1   40@YY
     I                                        5   60@MM
     I                                        7   80@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80DASKHZ
     I                                        1   40DASKYY
     I                                        5   60DASKMM
     I                                        7   80DASKDD
      *
     C           KEYHIN    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN1
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN2
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN3
      *
     C           KEYDA1    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN1
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN2
     C                     KFLD           AHHIN3
     C                     KFLD           #KUBN   1
     C                     KFLD           #KHYMD  80
     C*------------------------------------------*
     C*     臨出データ抽出                     *
     C*------------------------------------------*
      *
      *
     C                     Z-ADDAHYMD     #KHYMD
     C                     MOVE 'R'       #KUBN
      *
     C           KEYDA1    SETLLADATL601
     C                     SETOF                     8198
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    NOTFND  1
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEYHIN    READEADATL601                 81
     C                     SETOF                     66
     C           *IN81     IFEQ '0'
     C           DASKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           DASKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     66
     C                     END
      *
     C           *IN66     IFEQ '0'
     C           *IN81     ANDEQ'0'
      *
     C           DAKUBN    IFEQ 'R'
     C                     SETON                     98U2
     C                     EXCPTF01
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
     C  N81                END
     C           *IN98     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE '1'       NOTFND
     C                     SETOF                       U2
     C                     EXCPTF02
     C                     END
      *
     OAH#WP3I E                F01
     O                         AHHIN1     5
     O                         AHHIN2    10
     O                         AHHIN3    12
     O                         DAMAIS    15
     O                         DAHTYY    19
     O                         DAHTMM    21
     O                         DAHTDD    23
     O                         DAHTBB    25
